This package contains a modules to manipulate SIRTX font files.

SIRTX font files are bitmap fonts used by the SIRTX operating system.

This package contains SIRTX::Font to manipulate such font files and basic tools to allow such operation from the command line:
- sf-merge to manipulate files
- sf-to-html to generate nice HTML summaries of fonts
- sf-render which performs a very basic (and limited) rendering using the given font
